## App Milestones
Building Apps step-by-step


### Milestones
1. PROJECT - Create new project
2. PAGE - Create app page
3. DATA - Create database connection and CRUD
4. VIEWS - Create subscriber Views
5. CONTROLLER - Create subscriber business logic


### 1. PROJECT
* Create new project
* Apache, MySQL local servers
* Version control
* Test links in browser (local, remote)
* Data admin links (local, remote)


### 2. PAGE
* Create app page
* General page template
* Organization of pages
* Structure of code


### 3. DATA
* Create database connection
* Create database (local, remote)
* Setup general connection function
* Create database table for model
* Design data model
* Create subscriber CRUD functions


### 4. VIEWS
* Create subscriber Views
* Create views (list, details, add, update, delete)
* Encapsulate in views for each data type


### 5. CONTROLLER
* Create subscriber Controller
* Call the DB or views
* Handle page sequence
* Handle errors
